# Reduces Docker build context (faster builds + smaller images).
# Anything not listed here is sent to the daemon and considered for the image.

# Build outputs / caches
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.cache

# Test artifacts
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/screenshots
**/__diff_output__

# Dev infra
.git
.github
.cursor
.cursorrules
.vscode
.idea

# Supabase local
supabase/.temp
supabase/.branches
supabase/seed.sql

# Local environment & secrets — NEVER bake into the image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# Misc
**/.DS_Store
**/tmp
**/temp
**/uploads
docs
README.md
*.md
!Dockerfile
actions.jsonl
